### HTML page
GET http://localhost:8090/

### Full DOT graph
GET http://localhost:8090/api/graph

### All entries
GET http://localhost:8090/api/entries

### Unique kinds
GET http://localhost:8090/api/kinds

### Unique namespaces
GET http://localhost:8090/api/namespaces

### Active edge rules
GET http://localhost:8090/api/rules

### Filter by kind (HTTP layer)
GET http://localhost:8090/api/graph?kind=http.*

### Filter by kind (functions)
GET http://localhost:8090/api/graph?kind=function.lua

### Filter by namespace
GET http://localhost:8090/api/graph?ns=app

### Focus on entry
GET http://localhost:8090/api/graph?entry=app:router

### Focus with depth
GET http://localhost:8090/api/graph?entry=app:router&depth=2

### Focus outgoing only
GET http://localhost:8090/api/graph?entry=app:router&dir=out

### Focus incoming only
GET http://localhost:8090/api/graph?entry=app:router&dir=in

### Orphans only
GET http://localhost:8090/api/graph?orphans=true

### Combined: kind + namespace
GET http://localhost:8090/api/graph?kind=function.lua&ns=app
